{"bangumi":{"date":"2005-04-02","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/91/d5/20026_NSFFL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/91/d5/20026_NSFFL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/91/d5/20026_NSFFL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/91/d5/20026_NSFFL.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/91/d5/20026_NSFFL.jpg"},"summary":"《出云战记》是以Studio e.go!公司制作的游戏《IZUMO》为原作的电视动画。2005年4月至6月播放。 八岐猛是一个性格单纯又直率的少年。他的生活似乎从很小的时候就已经模式化了：每天早上被青梅竹马的白鸟姐妹里的明日香用各种飞身飞脚叫起床，然后再把姐姐琴乃做的早饭吃光，接着出门与幼年起的玩伴大斗刚打过招呼后匆忙上学。这样的生活已经千篇一律让人觉得没什么新奇可言了。\r\n\r\n然而在一场地震过后，八岐猛的校园生活就有了翻天覆地的彻底改变。学校顷刻间在地震中化为了废墟，随之出现的是一群恐怖的异形怪物，接着又从校舍中涌出了一群身着日本古代服装的奇怪人士——为了恢复现代社会的面貌，猛不得不开始了残酷的战斗……","name":"IZUMO -猛き剣の閃記-","name_cn":"出云战记","tags":[{"name":"后宫","count":41,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山本大妈","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005年4月","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"里番","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"EGO","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神兽","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中川聡","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2005年","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"穿越","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改编","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动漫","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"优先级G","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"スタジオ九魔","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日漫","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冨永恒雄","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补标","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"季番組","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":